1
00:00:07,024 --> 00:00:11,380
[The 21st Seoul International Culinary Competition]

2
00:00:14,906 --> 00:00:18,670
[Do Ye Seok]

3
00:00:20,896 --> 00:00:22,900
- Hello?
- Yeon Du is injured.

4
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:24,533
You need to come here.

5
00:00:24,533 --> 00:00:26,159
What?

6
00:00:35,978 --> 00:00:39,163
I was dragging you down.

7
00:00:41,367 --> 00:00:44,060
That's why I wanted to break up.

8
00:00:45,254 --> 00:00:48,170
This is the best for us.

9
00:00:52,811 --> 00:00:54,304
Hey, Ji Hyeon Ho!

10
00:00:54,304 --> 00:00:57,330
Where are you going again? Hey!

11
00:01:11,071 --> 00:01:15,775
[Best Mistake 3]

12
00:01:15,775 --> 00:01:17,577
Kim Yeon Du!

13
00:01:21,256 --> 00:01:23,207
I'm sorry.

14
00:01:25,202 --> 00:01:27,503
He said she was at the nurse's office.

15
00:01:29,890 --> 00:01:31,816
Hyeon Ho.

16
00:01:36,063 --> 00:01:38,309
Are you okay? Are you hurt badly?

17
00:01:38,309 --> 00:01:39,708
Where and how much did you get hurt?

18
00:01:39,708 --> 00:01:42,393
It's just a minor bruise.

19
00:01:43,228 --> 00:01:45,379
No need to worry.

20
00:01:48,626 --> 00:01:51,027
How did you get injured?

21
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,988
Did something happen?

22
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:57,870
That was...

23
00:02:10,522 --> 00:02:11,723
[A few hours ago]

24
00:02:11,723 --> 00:02:13,150
What's wrong with you?

25
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:15,684
Let go of me.

26
00:02:15,684 --> 00:02:19,004
The one who locked up Yeon Du that day. It was you, wasn't it?

27
00:02:19,004 --> 00:02:20,665
What?

28
00:02:35,372 --> 00:02:38,048
Did you think you'd never get caught?

29
00:02:39,001 --> 00:02:42,701
Why? What did she do to you?

30
00:02:43,881 --> 00:02:47,748
Yes, I did it.

31
00:02:49,178 --> 00:02:53,979
So what? It's all in the past.

32
00:02:56,251 --> 00:02:58,900
How low are you going?

33
00:03:00,397 --> 00:03:02,257
This isn't like you.

34
00:03:02,257 --> 00:03:04,784
What do you know about me?

35
00:03:05,569 --> 00:03:07,670
Do you know who I really am?

36
00:03:07,670 --> 00:03:10,206
What do you want to say?

37
00:03:11,183 --> 00:03:14,284
You don't know who I really am.

38
00:03:14,995 --> 00:03:18,860
I was busy hiding myself while I went out with you.

39
00:03:20,334 --> 00:03:22,235
You were from a good family with a smart brain.

40
00:03:22,235 --> 00:03:24,396
All the professors and students liked you.

41
00:03:24,396 --> 00:03:28,220
I became so small next to you who had it all.

42
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:33,750
But I was too busy pretending I was okay.

43
00:03:35,749 --> 00:03:38,018
And yet...

44
00:03:38,018 --> 00:03:41,971
You felt upset that I went to the internship instead of you?

45
00:03:42,972 --> 00:03:45,374
You already knew everything.

46
00:03:46,129 --> 00:03:49,421
I had to work two to three part-time jobs and I was desperate to get the scholarship.

47
00:03:49,421 --> 00:03:52,607
And I still worried I wasn't good enough to get a decent job.

48
00:03:52,607 --> 00:03:55,242
You already knew.

49
00:03:55,242 --> 00:03:59,086
You knew how much I wanted that internship.

50
00:03:59,086 --> 00:04:00,015
Jin Se Hui.

51
00:04:00,015 --> 00:04:02,516
Kim Yeon Du is just the same.

52
00:04:04,044 --> 00:04:07,071
She doesn't have to try hard and yet she gets everything.

53
00:04:07,948 --> 00:04:11,125
Everyone takes care of her and protects her.

54
00:04:12,202 --> 00:04:13,928
It's annoying.

55
00:04:13,928 --> 00:04:17,913
That's why I did it, because she was so annoying.

56
00:04:17,913 --> 00:04:21,075
Why not? Can't I do that?

57
00:04:22,729 --> 00:04:25,222
It was yours.

58
00:04:28,177 --> 00:04:29,802
What?

59
00:04:29,802 --> 00:04:34,012
The internship, it was yours anyway.

60
00:04:36,226 --> 00:04:38,411
Even if you hadn't taken my application away,

61
00:04:38,411 --> 00:04:40,588
you would've gotten it.

62
00:04:40,588 --> 00:04:43,557
It was yours to begin with.

63
00:04:51,917 --> 00:04:53,199
Se Hui?
[SEATTLE CASTLA Final Application for Overseas Internship:
Hwayang Univ. Year 1, Do Ye Seok]

64
00:04:53,210 --> 00:04:54,039
Yes.

65
00:04:54,049 --> 00:04:56,037
I'm on my way from Professor Park's office.

66
00:04:56,037 --> 00:05:00,214
Se Hui, she really set her mind into it.

67
00:05:00,214 --> 00:05:04,205
Her portfolio was no joke.

68
00:05:04,205 --> 00:05:08,397
CASTLA also pointed her out and wanted her to come.

69
00:05:08,397 --> 00:05:10,484
Wow, is that true?

70
00:05:10,484 --> 00:05:12,069
Huh?

71
00:05:12,069 --> 00:05:13,213
You like it?

72
00:05:13,213 --> 00:05:14,755
So much?

73
00:05:14,755 --> 00:05:17,783
If Se Hui gets it, you don't, and you still like it?

74
00:05:17,783 --> 00:05:19,119
Of course.

75
00:05:19,119 --> 00:05:22,912
Se Hui has worked so hard for this.

76
00:05:22,912 --> 00:05:24,982
You're so nice, aren't you?

77
00:05:25,767 --> 00:05:28,191
Hey, it's a secret.

78
00:05:28,191 --> 00:05:30,637
So act natural. Okay?

79
00:05:30,637 --> 00:05:32,373
Yes.

80
00:05:33,792 --> 00:05:36,085
Stop smiling.

81
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:43,368
So please just stop.

82
00:05:43,368 --> 00:05:45,736
You're not like this.

83
00:05:45,736 --> 00:05:48,539
Stop hating yourself.

84
00:05:49,149 --> 00:05:53,592
The person you hate is not Yeon Du, but yourself.

85
00:05:56,657 --> 00:06:00,599
As I said before, I forgot about it all.

86
00:06:00,599 --> 00:06:02,879
So you do, too.

87
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:05,589
Just forget it and live your life.

88
00:06:07,684 --> 00:06:10,002
I'm speaking from my heart.

89
00:07:10,163 --> 00:07:12,631
Unni Se Hui. Unni Se Hui!

90
00:07:12,631 --> 00:07:14,167
Are you alright?

91
00:07:14,167 --> 00:07:16,060
Unni Se Hui.

92
00:07:22,476 --> 00:07:26,612
Why are you here, Hyeon Ho? What about the competition?

93
00:07:27,414 --> 00:07:29,918
Well, I pulled out of it.

94
00:07:29,918 --> 00:07:32,375
Hey! What do you mean, "Pulled out?"

95
00:07:32,375 --> 00:07:34,003
Have you still lost your mind?

96
00:07:34,003 --> 00:07:36,070
What are you going to do if you act like this again?

97
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:40,030
Why are you here? Have you really lost your mind?

98
00:07:44,890 --> 00:07:47,132
Listen carefully, Kim Yeon Du.

99
00:07:48,585 --> 00:07:51,971
My choice is always you, then and now.

100
00:07:52,773 --> 00:07:55,850
That's why I wanted to enter the culinary competition.

101
00:08:02,824 --> 00:08:04,508
What?

102
00:08:04,508 --> 00:08:07,527
I wanted to transfer here.

103
00:08:07,527 --> 00:08:10,515
I wanted to get closer in distance.

104
00:08:10,515 --> 00:08:14,243
And I also wanted to become a better person to suit you.

105
00:08:15,712 --> 00:08:20,722
But in order to transfer, I needed an award.

106
00:08:20,722 --> 00:08:23,600
That's why I entered into the culinary competition.

107
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:30,075
That's not what I wanted from you.

108
00:08:30,075 --> 00:08:31,111
What?

109
00:08:31,111 --> 00:08:36,453
Hyeon Ho, I choose who suits me.

110
00:08:36,453 --> 00:08:41,768
No matter what school you go to or what grades or awards you have.

111
00:08:41,768 --> 00:08:45,110
That's not important to me at all.

112
00:08:47,644 --> 00:08:51,295
Because it's you, I like you because you're Ji Hyeon Ho.

113
00:08:51,295 --> 00:08:52,596
Same here.

114
00:08:52,596 --> 00:08:55,693
Because it's you, Kim Yeon Du.

115
00:08:55,693 --> 00:09:01,880
Even if the same thing happens 100 or 1,000 times, you always come first.

116
00:09:02,843 --> 00:09:04,777
Hyeon Ho...

117
00:09:07,973 --> 00:09:10,816
So stop getting injured.

118
00:09:10,816 --> 00:09:13,177
It scares me.

119
00:09:15,046 --> 00:09:17,039
All right.

120
00:09:37,194 --> 00:09:39,981
- How is Yeon Du?
- Why did you do that?

121
00:09:39,981 --> 00:09:43,164
You and Yeon Du might have been seriously injured.

122
00:09:43,164 --> 00:09:45,950
You should've at least told me.

123
00:09:51,625 --> 00:09:53,493
What's with those two?

124
00:09:53,493 --> 00:09:56,286
So how is Yeon Du now?

125
00:09:56,286 --> 00:09:59,805
Is she okay? She didn't get hurt?

126
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:04,211
I should go see her.

127
00:10:04,211 --> 00:10:06,113
What are you going to tell her?

128
00:10:06,113 --> 00:10:10,002
Tell her everything and say you're sorry?

129
00:10:10,002 --> 00:10:12,069
Well...

130
00:10:12,954 --> 00:10:15,264
Leaving her behind on the trip.

131
00:10:15,264 --> 00:10:18,553
Locking her up in the darkroom and even this...

132
00:10:18,553 --> 00:10:21,395
She would never think you're behind it all.

133
00:10:21,395 --> 00:10:23,931
Jin Se Hui, that little...

134
00:10:28,053 --> 00:10:31,171
She thinks of you as a good senior.

135
00:10:32,035 --> 00:10:35,392
She'll get hurt when she finds out.

136
00:10:35,392 --> 00:10:38,530
Thank you for your concern, Senior.

137
00:10:45,628 --> 00:10:46,821
Yeon Du.

138
00:10:46,821 --> 00:10:52,389
But you know I'll handle my pain.

139
00:10:56,982 --> 00:10:59,616
Could I have a word with you?

140
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:17,749
Was it really all your doing?

141
00:11:19,187 --> 00:11:21,071
The incidents on the trip, the darkroom,

142
00:11:21,071 --> 00:11:26,182
even today. Was it really all your doing?

143
00:11:29,364 --> 00:11:31,381
Why did you?

144
00:11:31,381 --> 00:11:34,376
Why did you hate me so much?

145
00:11:35,103 --> 00:11:37,746
You were annoying.

146
00:11:37,746 --> 00:11:39,531
What?

147
00:11:40,391 --> 00:11:43,819
Do Ye Seok and Ji Hyeon Ho both liked you.

148
00:11:43,819 --> 00:11:46,955
Everyone in the department praised you.

149
00:11:48,705 --> 00:11:51,210
It was so annoying.

150
00:11:51,861 --> 00:11:54,362
What did you say?

151
00:11:54,362 --> 00:11:58,225
I had to work so hard to hear such compliments.

152
00:11:58,225 --> 00:12:00,552
But you did nothing—

153
00:12:01,371 --> 00:12:03,313
No.

154
00:12:03,313 --> 00:12:06,792
You just had it all from the start.

155
00:12:07,828 --> 00:12:11,703
It was unfair and frustrating.

156
00:12:15,018 --> 00:12:17,994
How can you be so sure?

157
00:12:17,994 --> 00:12:19,396
What?

158
00:12:19,396 --> 00:12:21,332
You're wrong to say I did nothing.

159
00:12:21,332 --> 00:12:24,685
And I didn't have it all from the start.

160
00:12:24,685 --> 00:12:29,998
You can't just take someone's heart even if you want to.

161
00:12:32,207 --> 00:12:35,371
I don't know how hard you worked for it.

162
00:12:35,371 --> 00:12:38,282
But I didn't get it easy either.

163
00:12:38,282 --> 00:12:43,500
It all needed time and effort for such relationships.

164
00:12:46,858 --> 00:12:49,810
So don't underestimate me.

165
00:12:51,362 --> 00:12:56,422
My time and effort, you don't know them.

166
00:12:57,285 --> 00:13:00,152
No, I don't know.

167
00:13:01,356 --> 00:13:04,392
But you still had everything I didn't.

168
00:13:04,392 --> 00:13:07,327
And you were so annoying.

169
00:13:08,213 --> 00:13:10,314
Now, are you satisfied?

170
00:13:14,511 --> 00:13:17,796
Then why did you save me?

171
00:13:17,796 --> 00:13:21,373
- Well...
- Didn't you worry about me, too?

172
00:13:21,373 --> 00:13:23,435
That's the truth.

173
00:13:23,435 --> 00:13:26,789
You helped me on the first day we met.

174
00:13:26,789 --> 00:13:31,816
That's the real you and the arm shows your true heart.

175
00:13:31,816 --> 00:13:33,770
Isn't it?

176
00:13:34,906 --> 00:13:37,007
Is that so important?

177
00:13:37,742 --> 00:13:40,752
You were constantly in trouble because of me.

178
00:13:40,752 --> 00:13:42,413
Even today, you nearly injured yourself seriously.

179
00:13:42,413 --> 00:13:44,689
You're right.

180
00:13:44,689 --> 00:13:46,834
That's why I'm upset.

181
00:13:49,062 --> 00:13:51,371
So apologize.

182
00:13:53,642 --> 00:13:56,501
Not just with words.

183
00:13:57,195 --> 00:14:00,364
Show me your truth in person.

184
00:14:04,202 --> 00:14:06,370
I'm still upset.

185
00:14:06,370 --> 00:14:10,930
So slowly, with time,

186
00:14:11,526 --> 00:14:13,910
apologize to me.

187
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:16,488
I'll be watching you by staying next to you.

188
00:14:49,255 --> 00:14:51,807
I hope nothing goes wrong.

189
00:14:53,459 --> 00:14:55,869
You don't have to worry.

190
00:15:00,742 --> 00:15:03,510
Kim Yeon Du is stronger than you think.

191
00:15:10,501 --> 00:15:13,078
Call it even with this.

192
00:15:13,078 --> 00:15:14,730
What?

193
00:15:15,757 --> 00:15:18,459
I'm not trying to stand on pride.

194
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:23,020
I'm too shy to say thanks or sorry.

195
00:15:24,432 --> 00:15:26,642
So just call it even.

196
00:15:26,642 --> 00:15:28,568
You just did.

197
00:15:29,562 --> 00:15:30,679
Pardon?

198
00:15:30,679 --> 00:15:34,564
Apologizing and being grateful. You just said it all.

199
00:15:35,485 --> 00:15:37,885
Well I was just saying...

200
00:15:37,885 --> 00:15:39,463
You don't have to apologize.

201
00:15:39,463 --> 00:15:41,381
And no need to thank me.

202
00:15:42,008 --> 00:15:43,709
I was just explaining...

203
00:15:43,709 --> 00:15:45,819
I'm also grateful.

204
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,710
What's with him?

205
00:16:36,128 --> 00:16:38,281
Senior.

206
00:16:38,281 --> 00:16:40,340
What are you doing here alone?

207
00:16:40,340 --> 00:16:44,925
Well, I was looking at Life4cuts from the festival.

208
00:16:44,925 --> 00:16:48,807
We'll be awarding the best cut among these pictures.

209
00:16:48,807 --> 00:16:52,217
But everything looks so good.

210
00:16:52,217 --> 00:16:54,963
It's hard to choose.

211
00:16:54,963 --> 00:16:59,218
It's really, your life in four cuts.

212
00:17:20,256 --> 00:17:22,624
- Senior Ye Seok—
- I found.

213
00:17:26,054 --> 00:17:27,988
The best one.

214
00:17:36,689 --> 00:17:39,221
Senior Ye Seok, I have something to tell you.

215
00:17:39,221 --> 00:17:40,934
I already know.

216
00:17:41,736 --> 00:17:43,336
Excuse me?

217
00:17:43,963 --> 00:17:47,593
What you're trying to say. I already know.

218
00:17:53,289 --> 00:17:55,874
The answer to my confession.

219
00:17:56,709 --> 00:18:01,027
You're trying to say it right now.

220
00:18:03,674 --> 00:18:06,726
You're refusing me, of course.

221
00:18:07,778 --> 00:18:09,529
Right?

222
00:18:12,125 --> 00:18:14,342
I'm sorry.

223
00:18:32,336 --> 00:18:36,022
[Hyeon Ho♥]

224
00:18:36,022 --> 00:18:37,916
Go.

225
00:18:37,916 --> 00:18:40,385
I'll take care of the rest.

226
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,941
Okay.

227
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:54,007
But...

228
00:18:57,003 --> 00:18:59,329
I won't be rooting for you.

229
00:19:02,442 --> 00:19:04,768
If you two break up again,

230
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:08,872
I don't know what I would do.

231
00:19:41,864 --> 00:19:44,200
[Congrats on graduation, Ah Hun.]
[Kang Ah Hun, You're An Adult Now!]

232
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:46,652
Those two won't stop until Yeon Du comes.

233
00:19:46,652 --> 00:19:49,229
I'll call her to see where she is.

234
00:19:53,784 --> 00:19:55,010
Squirtle!

235
00:19:55,010 --> 00:19:56,778
Yeon Du!

236
00:20:00,208 --> 00:20:02,201
I thought you weren't coming.

237
00:20:02,201 --> 00:20:05,028
Sorry, I had to stop by the school.

238
00:20:05,028 --> 00:20:06,296
Hurry and sit.

239
00:20:06,296 --> 00:20:09,180
There is a seat next to your boyfriend.

240
00:20:21,521 --> 00:20:23,402
- You're here.
- Yes.

241
00:20:23,402 --> 00:20:26,043
- Sorry, I'm late.
- It's alright.

242
00:20:31,188 --> 00:20:33,131
Why is everyone so late?

243
00:20:51,668 --> 00:20:54,390
- Look at them having fun.
- Yes.

244
00:21:30,881 --> 00:21:32,457
Listen up.

245
00:21:32,457 --> 00:21:36,343
As the president of the photo club, I can't just let go on a day like this.

246
00:21:36,343 --> 00:21:37,871
The photograph...

247
00:21:37,871 --> 00:21:40,356
Let's take it here. All good?

248
00:21:40,356 --> 00:21:42,730
Of course. Come on out.

249
00:21:50,084 --> 00:21:53,693
Okay, I'll shoot.

250
00:21:53,693 --> 00:21:57,034
Everyone, get closer.

251
00:21:59,093 --> 00:22:01,277
I'll shoot.

252
00:22:04,970 --> 00:22:07,730
Ten, night.

253
00:22:07,730 --> 00:22:09,170
Eight.

254
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:10,354
Kim Yeon Du.

255
00:22:10,354 --> 00:22:11,919
Yes?

256
00:22:11,919 --> 00:22:14,600
Is it you? My girlfriend?

257
00:22:17,011 --> 00:22:19,770
Hey, what's with the kiss?

258
00:22:19,770 --> 00:22:22,373
- Ji Hyeon Ho.
- Yes?

259
00:22:22,373 --> 00:22:25,350
Is it you? My boyfriend?

260
00:22:28,372 --> 00:22:32,356
Yes, correct. I'm your boyfriend.

261
00:22:35,145 --> 00:22:37,060
Hold on!

262
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:40,100
I'm not used to this.

263
00:22:46,607 --> 00:22:48,725
What's with you two!

264
00:22:51,295 --> 00:22:53,337
Ah Hun.

265
00:22:53,337 --> 00:22:55,324
Where's my baseball bat?

266
00:22:55,324 --> 00:22:57,641
Over there.

267
00:23:02,940 --> 00:23:06,092
It's been an insane semester.

268
00:23:06,092 --> 00:23:08,948
Now, a new season is almost here on campus.

269
00:23:08,948 --> 00:23:10,029
No, I don't.

270
00:23:10,029 --> 00:23:10,845
Let's have lunch together first.

271
00:23:10,845 --> 00:23:11,927
- When you think about it...
- Sure!

272
00:23:11,937 --> 00:23:14,501
Time is very odd.

273
00:23:14,501 --> 00:23:16,995
It is equally given to everyone.

274
00:23:16,995 --> 00:23:19,570
But it passes by differently for everyone.

275
00:23:19,570 --> 00:23:22,460
That's not even close.

276
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:23,365
I'm accepted!

277
00:23:23,365 --> 00:23:25,353
Congratulations!

278
00:23:26,222 --> 00:23:29,030
Some kinds of time end.

279
00:23:31,894 --> 00:23:35,260
And other times start again.

280
00:23:40,269 --> 00:23:43,980
It matures for some.

281
00:23:49,253 --> 00:23:51,787
Here's the officer's notebook.

282
00:23:51,787 --> 00:23:53,773
Is it you?

283
00:23:53,773 --> 00:23:55,525
My vice president?

284
00:23:56,318 --> 00:23:58,369
What are you saying?

285
00:23:59,113 --> 00:24:01,965
Thanks in advance, Vice President.

286
00:24:01,965 --> 00:24:02,728
Sure.

287
00:24:02,738 --> 00:24:03,567
Hug me once?

288
00:24:03,578 --> 00:24:05,485
- No.
- Yes? Okay?

289
00:24:05,485 --> 00:24:06,398
Go away.

290
00:24:06,408 --> 00:24:08,112
Hug me, hurry.

291
00:24:08,112 --> 00:24:13,240
And for others, it gradually fades away.

292
00:24:15,821 --> 00:24:21,307
In the midst of time passing, we change

293
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:25,922
or stay the same.

294
00:24:27,391 --> 00:24:30,733
What's important is that through those times,

295
00:24:30,733 --> 00:24:34,347
we are slowly maturing.

296
00:24:35,383 --> 00:24:40,336
Love isn't just a heartbeat.

297
00:24:40,336 --> 00:24:42,847
Now we understand.

298
00:24:42,847 --> 00:24:47,058
Feeling sorry, grateful, hurt, and sad,

299
00:24:47,058 --> 00:24:50,179
it was all love.

300
00:24:50,179 --> 00:24:56,666
Little by little, we are learning different forms of love.

301
00:24:58,322 --> 00:25:05,041
The past is meaningful and the future is exciting

302
00:25:05,738 --> 00:25:09,207
because I was not alone through it all.

303
00:25:09,207 --> 00:25:11,926
It was our time together.

304
00:25:23,973 --> 00:25:28,536
Throughout my eighteenth, nineteenth and twentieth year.

305
00:25:28,536 --> 00:25:31,029
Thanks for being with me.

306
00:25:31,950 --> 00:25:36,940
Channel manager biolince!

307
