00:25:51,970 --> 00:25:56,190
Thanks to all language moderators, editors, and translators!

311
00:25:56,190 --> 00:25:58,447
Can we go one more time?

312
00:25:58,447 --> 00:26:02,940
I forgot it all.
♫ It gets back to the starting point ♫

313
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:04,600
Is it right?
♫ I'm going forward to you with steering helm ♫

314
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:10,990
Um... Jin...
♫ You know I'm getting closer ♫

315
00:26:10,990 --> 00:26:13,130
I'll buy you a drink if you make it in one take.

316
00:26:13,130 --> 00:26:15,300
♫ Run faster toward me ♫

317
00:26:15,309 --> 00:26:16,865
Why did you two break up?

318
00:26:16,865 --> 00:26:18,527
Um, can I do that over?

319
00:26:18,527 --> 00:26:19,653
I'll do that again.

320
00:26:19,653 --> 00:26:20,854
No... No way.

321
00:26:20,854 --> 00:26:22,298
I don't think that's an okay cut.

322
00:26:22,298 --> 00:26:24,191
Don't you have any pride?

323
00:26:24,191 --> 00:26:27,956
I'm sorry. I'll do that over.
♫ Sometimes I know or don't know, it's strange ♫

324
00:26:27,956 --> 00:26:28,910
I'm sorry.

325
00:26:28,910 --> 00:26:34,670
♫ Even if it hurts, we still cross the lines ♫

326
00:26:34,670 --> 00:26:36,680
Oh, then...

327
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:40,820
♫ Like being possessed by something ♫

328
00:26:40,820 --> 00:26:43,440
♫ It's getting perfect again ♫

329
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:46,346
Oppa. I said, "Oppa instead of Senior."

330
00:26:46,346 --> 00:26:49,290
The call isn't going through.

331
00:26:49,290 --> 00:26:52,680
Are you really out of your mind?!

332
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:55,770
♫ I really wanna like you ♫

333
00:26:55,770 --> 00:27:00,410
♫ Even though I don't expect it'll last forever ♫

334
00:27:00,410 --> 00:27:03,260
♫ It's hard ♫

335
00:27:03,260 --> 00:27:05,380
♫ It changes from 0 to 100 ♫

336
00:27:05,380 --> 00:27:06,710
♫ More than several dozens times a day ♫

337
00:27:06,710 --> 00:27:07,985
I'm sorry for being snobby.

338
00:27:07,985 --> 00:27:11,486
Let's do again.

339
00:27:11,486 --> 00:27:12,290
I'll do that over.

340
00:27:12,290 --> 00:27:17,420
♫ I'm getting hot ♫
♫ I'm losing my mind again ♫

341
00:27:17,420 --> 00:27:20,760
Yes, let's do again.
♫ Hold me, you know ♫

342
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:26,130
♫ As much as you believe me, I'm falling into you ♫

